    <FactionDef ParentName="OCARINA_MantledBeastsFactionRoughBase">
        <defName>OCARINA_MantledBeastsRough</defName>
        <label>va'ji splinter</label>
        <description>These people haven't been here for long, spreading across the rim rapidly with their more advanced technology. Weaker than the larger colonies, this group was pulled into the freedom of the rim and chose to live on their own, perpetuating the cycles of violence their home systems try to mediate.\n\nThese people take what they can, when they can, with as much force as can be exerted.</description>
        <factionIconPath>World/WorldObjects/Expanding/VajiRough</factionIconPath>
